Dou Dou.

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:26.960
Pulanglah bersamaku, oke?

00:29:27.520 --> 00:29:30.160
Saya ingin bermain dengan Bibi.

00:29:31.280 --> 00:29:32.360
Tante?

00:29:38.960 --> 00:29:39.960
Dou Dou.

00:29:40.320 --> 00:29:41.520
Pulanglah bersama ibumu.

00:29:41.600 --> 00:29:43.439
Lain kali
pamanmu dan aku mengunjungi kamu,

00:29:43.440 --> 00:29:45.519
Kami akan membawakanmu
banyak figur gula, oke?

00:29:45.520 --> 00:29:46.840
Anda bisa memakannya sekaligus.

